'''孙崧''' （{{bd|1987年||}}），男，[[安徽|安徽]][[怀宁|怀宁]]人，中国数学家。

== 生平 ==
1987年出生于[[安徽|安徽]][[怀宁县|怀宁县]]。2002年进入[[中国科学技术大学|中国科学技术大学]][[少年班|少年班]]。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ustcif.org/default.php/content/4053/|title=陈秀雄孙崧荣获维布伦奖|date=2018-11-20|website=University of Science and Technology of China Initiative Foundation|access-date=2019-04-09|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602235337/https://www.ustcif.org/default.php/content/4053/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2006年赴美留学进入[[威斯康辛大學麥迪遜分校|威斯康辛大學麥迪遜分校]]，2010年获得[[微分几何学|微分几何学]]博士学位，<ref name=":1" /><ref name="stonybrook">{{cite web|url=https://news.stonybrook.edu/newsroom/press-release/general/2182014songsun/|title=Song Sun Awarded Prestigious Sloan Fellowship for Mathematics|date=2014-02-18|website=Stony Brook University|accessdate=2019-04-03|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403203304/https://news.stonybrook.edu/newsroom/press-release/general/2182014songsun/|dead-url=no}}</ref>师从美国华人数学家[[陈秀雄_(数学家)|陈秀雄]]。<ref name="nodak">{{cite web|url=https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=144609|title=Song Sun|website=The Mathematics Genealogy Project|accessdate=2019-04-03|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403203945/https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=144609|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后进入[[倫敦帝國學院|倫敦帝國學院]]任教，2013年进入[[石溪大學|石溪大學]]担任助教。<ref name="stonybrook" />2018年进入[[加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校|加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校]]担任数学系副教授。<ref name="berkeley">{{cite web|url=https://math.berkeley.edu/people/faculty/song-sun|title=Song Sun|website=Department of Mathematics, University of California Berkeley|accessdate=2019-04-03|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119091826/https://math.berkeley.edu/people/faculty/song-sun|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 奖项和荣誉 ==
* 2014年获得[[斯隆奖|斯隆奖]]。<ref name="stonybrook" />
* 2018年受邀成为在[[巴西|巴西]][[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]举办的[[国际数学家大会|国际数学家大会]]演讲嘉宾。<ref name="icm2018">{{cite web|url=http://www.icm2018.org/portal/invited-section-lectures-speakers.html|title=Invited Section Lectures Speakers|website=ICM 2018|accessdate=2019-04-03|archive-date=2020-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221010438/http://www.icm2018.org/portal/invited-section-lectures-speakers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 2019年获得[[奥斯瓦尔德·维布伦几何学奖|奥斯瓦尔德·维布伦几何学奖]]，与[[西蒙·唐纳森|西蒙·唐纳森]]和导师[[陈秀雄_(数学家)|陈秀雄]]同时获奖。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ams.org/news?news_id=4705|title=2019 Oswald Veblen Prize in Geometry to Xiuxiong Chen, Simon Donaldson, and Song Sun|date=2018-11-19|website=American Mathematical Society|access-date=2019-04-09|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116092352/http://www.ams.org/news?news_id=4705|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="berkeley2">{{cite web|url=https://math.berkeley.edu/news/song-sun-receive-2019-oswald-veblen-prize-geometry-congratulations|title=Song Sun to receive the 2019 Oswald Veblen Prize in Geometry. Congratulations!|website=Department of Mathematics, University of California Berkeley|accessdate=2019-04-03|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403203413/https://math.berkeley.edu/news/song-sun-receive-2019-oswald-veblen-prize-geometry-congratulations|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 2021年荣获[[数学突破奖|数学突破奖]]新视野数学奖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://breakthroughprize.org/News/60 |title=Breakthrough Prize in Mathematics 2021 |access-date=2021-02-28 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126081730/https://breakthroughprize.org/News/60 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

